description:
ExternalENodeBFunction: Metadata about external eNodeB functions in a radio access network.

dateTime: Timestamp of data record.
Area_Name: Geographic area of the eNodeB.
CellId: Unique identifier for the cell site.
Id2: Redundant cell site identifier.
Id3:  Ancillary identifier (likely unused or placeholder).
Id4:  Internal identifier potentially linking to other systems.
vsDataType:  Data type identifier.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of data format.
ExternalENodeBFunction.eNodeBId:  Unique identifier for the eNodeB.
ExternalENodeBFunction.userLabel: User-defined label (mostly empty).
ExternalENodeBFunction.externalENodeBFunctionId: Unique ID for the external function instance.
ExternalENodeBFunction.isRemoveAllowed: Flag indicating if removal is permitted.
ExternalENodeBFunction.pLMNId: PLMN ID (mostly empty).
ExternalENodeBFunction.eNodeBPlmnId: eNodeB PLMN ID (mostly empty).
ExternalENodeBFunction.eranUlCompVlanPortRef: Uplink compensation VLAN port reference (mostly empty).
ExternalENodeBFunction.eranLinkMaxRttDelay: Maximum round-trip time delay for the link.
ExternalENodeBFunction.eNBId:  eNodeB identifier (potentially different from ExternalENodeBFunction.eNodeBId).
ExternalENodeBFunction.timeOfCreation: Timestamp of function creation.
ExternalENodeBFunction.zzzTemporary7: Placeholder column.
ExternalENodeBFunction.zzzTemporary8: Placeholder column.
ExternalENodeBFunction.zzzTemporary9: Placeholder column.
ExternalENodeBFunction.eranPrioritizationDisabled: Flag indicating if prioritization is disabled.
ExternalENodeBFunction.ulTrigHoSupport: Support for uplink triggered handover.
ExternalENodeBFunction.timeOfLastModification: Timestamp of last modification.
ExternalENodeBFunction.eranVlanPortRef: VLAN port reference.
ExternalENodeBFunction.mfbiSupport: Support for MFBI (Multi-Frequency Band Integration).
ExternalENodeBFunction.zzzTemporary2: Placeholder column.
ExternalENodeBFunction.zzzTemporary3: Placeholder column.
ExternalENodeBFunction.createdBy: User or system that created the entry.
ExternalENodeBFunction.zzzTemporary4: Placeholder column.
ExternalENodeBFunction.zzzTemporary5: Placeholder column.
ExternalENodeBFunction.zzzTemporary6: Placeholder column.
ExternalENodeBFunction.lastModification: Type of last modification.
ExternalENodeBFunction.masterEnbFunctionId: Master eNodeB function ID (mostly empty).
ExternalENodeBFunction.eSCellCapacityScaling: eSCell capacity scaling factor.
